Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/sli67/dotfiles.git ~/dotfiles

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

